page.html:
I'm overly obsessed with cute Pokémon and especially Eeveelutions!




I stream almost daily, mostly 4K but I do 7k and k-shoot as well, come say hi :

Livestream/Twitch

I'm also the admin of the Rhythm Gamers team/group, if you stream mania games like osumania, stepmania, k-shoot, lr2, o2jam etc feel free to ask for an invite

I love to inspire new people to start with rhythm games, as well as help other players have more fun and get better


YouTube

When DT gave pp bonus... good times
